# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#  BotCraftAI — Environment Variables
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
#  GEMINI API KEY (optional but recommended)
#  ─────────────────────────────────────────
#  Without it:  Bot uses LOCAL RAG mode
#               → Keyword search through your training data
#               → Works offline, no account needed
#
#  With it:     Bot uses FULL GEMINI AI mode
#               → Understands context and natural language
#               → Answers intelligently from your training data
#               → FREE tier: 15 requests/minute, 1M tokens/day
#
#  How to get it (FREE):
#  1. Go to: https://aistudio.google.com
#  2. Sign in with Google
#  3. Click "Get API Key" → "Create API Key"
#  4. Copy the key (starts with AIza...)
#  5. Paste it below and remove the # from the next line
#  6. Restart dev server: npm run dev
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# VITE_GEMINI_API_KEY=AIzaSy...your_key_here...
